ementara itu, struktur RW dan RT berperan penting dalam menjembatani komunikasi antara pemerintah desa dengan warga masyarakat, serta menjadi pelaksana kegiatan sosial kemasyarakatan di lingkungan terkecil. Pembagian wilayah ini tidak hanya bertujuan untuk efektivitas administrasi, tetapi juga berfungsi sebagai pendekatan dalam pembangunan yang lebih merata dan berkeadilan. Melalui sistem ini, aspirasi dan kebutuhan masyarakat dapat dihimpun dengan lebih cepat dan akurat, serta penyaluran berbagai program pemerintah \u2013 seperti bantuan sosial, pembangunan infrastruktur, hingga pembinaan masyarakat \u2013 dapat dilakukan secara terstruktur dan tepat sasaran. Tabel 9 Pembagian Wilayah No Nama Dusun Jumlah RW Jumlah RT 1 Gudang 1 2 2 Wedungan 1 3 3 Bogor 1 3 4 Jati 1 1 5 Jarakan 1 1 6 Ngelo 1 1 7 Dawung 1 2 8 Jahen 1 3 Sumber Data Profil Desa Tahun 2025","","1.","Rumah Tidak Sehat","123.33","KK","1.00","KK","124.33","KK",""],["","","2.","Rumah Tidak Layak Huni","","Unit","","Unit","","Unit",""],["","","3.","Rumah Layak Huni","0.00","KK","0.00","","0.00","",""]],[["No","Nama Dusun","Jumlah RW","Jumlah RT"],["1","Gudang","1","2"],["2","Wedungan","1","3"],["3","Bogor","1","3"],["4","Jati","1","1"],["5","Jarakan","1","1"],["6","Ngelo","1","1"],["7","Dawung","1","2"],["8","Jahen","1","3"]]],"22":[[["No","Nama","Jabatan"],["1",".............................","Kepala Desa"],["2",".............................","Sekretaris Desa"],["3",".............................","Kasi Pemerintahan"],["4",".............................","Kasi Kesra"],["5",".............................","Kasi Pelayanan"],["6",".............................","Kaur Perencanaan"],["7",".............................","Kaur Umum dan TU"],["8",".............................","Kaur Keuangan"],["9",".............................","Kepala Dusun ........."],["10",".............................","Kepala Dusun ............."],["11",".............................","Kepala Dusun .........."],["12","...................